title: Ztime-passes: columns not always seperated

labels.name: T-compiler
labels.description: Relevant to the compiler team, which will review and decide on the PR/issue.

body:
Sometimes when compiling code with `-Ztime-passes`, there is no space between rss column and the pass-name column:
````

time: 0.000; rss: 110MB	liveness_and_intrinsic_checking
````
